data.description: ***MOTIVATED SELLER!!!  BIG PRICE REDUCTION!!!***   Welcome to your new dream home! This stunning property on Folio Way in Kissimmee offers an unparalleled blend of luxury, comfort, and convenience. Nestled in the tranquil Tapestry community, this immaculate residence presents an ideal opportunity for discerning homebuyers seeking the perfect place to call their own.  Step inside this elegant 3-bedroom, 2.5 bathroom townhouse, where you'll find an open and spacious floor plan designed for modern living. With plenty of living space, there's room for everyone to stretch out and enjoy.  The heart of this home is the gourmet kitchen featuring granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample cabinet space. It's a chef's delight, perfect for preparing family meals and hosting gatherings.  The generous master suite is a private retreat with a walk-in closet and a beautifully appointed ensuite bathroom. Relax and rejuvenate in your own oasis.  Enjoy the Florida sunshine year-round on your patio. Whether you're sipping your morning coffee or hosting a barbecue, this outdoor space is perfect for entertaining and unwinding.  Move-in ready - make this exceptional property your new home.  Schedule your showing today and seize this incredible opportunity to own a piece of paradise.
